frontend/.vite/
frontend/coverage/
frontend/.cache/
frontend/.svelte-kit/
frontend/.vercel/

### Testing ###
**/jest.config.js
**/vitest.config.ts
**/__snapshots__/
**/*.spec.js
**/*.test.js
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.test.ts

